translated: Klevenfeldt, Lars Erik, forest master, Borås. b. 30/12/01 in Uoklum, Gothenburg and Bohuslän. 1st m. 34 with Helena Källman. Children: Lars b. 35, Ulf 39. — Studied: the student exam at Gothenburg's higher real school in 21, forest master exam in 28. Employed at Boden's district in 28, at Timber A-B Dalarna in 29, forest administration in Gothenburg and Bohuslän county from 29-42, fuel controller in Älvsborg's northern district in 42, chief of the Southern Älvsborg County's forest owners' association since 431, managing director at Randin & Co. A-B in Borås. Board member in the Swedish Timber Association since 45, member of the association's board in the Sjuhäradsbygden region since 44, board substitute in the Southern Sweden's timber measurement association.
